This fixture is a small Go module for change_guard integration coverage
against gopls. broken.go contains a deliberate type error (assigning a string
to an int) so gopls reports an error-severity diagnostic and change_guard
returns a broken verdict.

-- go.mod --
module changeguardfixture

go 1.27

-- broken.go --
package main

func brokenValue() int {
	var n int = "not an int"
	return n
}
